creator: BW Design
descriptionHtml:
If your games use Unity Ads and you want to stay up to date with their performance, this app is just for you. It lets you see your revenue, started videos, finished videos, CPM and fill rate. It shows detailed charts of all the stats.

The app doesn't require any logins or passwords - just the the API key from your Unity Ads Dashboard. It works offline, letting you analyse your revenue even if you don't have an Internet connection.

Your stats are not sent anywhere and are kept only on your device. Neither the authors of the app nor anyone else have access to your private data.

If you're interested in the source code, you can find it on CodeCanyon:
https://codecanyon.net/item/unity-ads-stats/24158762
descriptionShort: Lets you view the stats of Unity Ads in your games - revenue, views, CMP, etc.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Fixed displaying incorrect stats in some rare cases.
Reduced transferred data and database size.
